HEADWORD: Cisatlantic
<hw>Cis`at*lan"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>cis-</ets> + <ets>Atlantic</ets>.]</ety> <def>On this side of the
Atlantic Ocean; -- used of the eastern or the western side, according to
the standpoint of the writer.</def> <rj><au>Story.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
